Description: IfMetrics monitor your Unix system with all running processes. When we find an error our state-of-art AI will automagically fix it.
Headquarters Regions: Greater Boston Area, East Coast, New England
Full Description: Always know what's happening with your servers. IfMetrics monitor your Unix system with all running processes. When we find an error our state-of-art AI will automagically fix it. PROACTIVE IfMetrics is an AI-powered tool that monitors your Unix system in realtime. It comes with a state-of-art AI, which helps you detect problems and irregularities on your system. Unlike other monitoring tools IfMetrics will automagically fix problems that are deemed to be harmful to your server. It is able to self-learn using concepts of self-supervised machine learning. It gives you the power of fixing your system yourself without ever having to contact a support person or engineer. PREDICT HEALTH You can use IfMetrics to monitor daemon processes or similar programs running on localhost. IfMetrics is particularly useful for monitoring daemon processes, such as those started at system boot time from /etc/init/ For instance sendmail, sshd, apache and mysql. FILES, DIRS AND FILESYSTEMS You can also use IfMetrics to monitor files, directories and filesystems on localhost. IfMetrics can monitor these items for changes, such as timestamps changes, checksum changes or size changes. This is also useful for security reasons - you can monitor the md5 or sha1 checksum of files that should not change and get an alert or perform an action if they should change.
Industry Groups: Artificial Intelligence (AI), Data and Analytics, Information Technology, Science and Engineering, Software

Full Description: Energy Asset Development markets and sells LED Lighting products. It acts as a distributor, but without carrying inventory. For these reasons, the Company decided to develop relations with several LED product manufacturers, concentrate marketing to projects, and meet demand by ordering from manufacturers based on project needs.  Project requirements are shipped directly to the project site by the manufacturing base. This strategy allows the company to stay competitive on pricing, as well as possess the ability to deploy the technology for the market. While the Company is focused on local markets at present, this business model allows the company to expand to a national scale seamlessly.

Description: GoodMouth improves health, prevents disease, and helps those in need by providing a unique toothbrush delivery subscription service.
Headquarters Regions: Greater New York Area, East Coast, Northeastern US
Full Description: GoodMouth improves health, prevents disease, and helps those in need by providing a unique toothbrush delivery subscription service that serves consumers, dental health professionals, and corporate benefits programs.  GoodMouth’s message is simple. Old toothbrushes are dirty and can cause easily preventable oral diseases which studies have found correlate to other serious health concerns such as heart disease and diabetes. And it’s not just a healthcare problem. Over 164 million hours of work and 50 million hours of school are lost every year due to oral health issues. GoodMouth provides consumers with the right brush at the right time, directly to their door. For dental health professionals, GoodMouth helps differentiate their practices and build stronger bonds with patients through the regular home delivery of toothbrushes, oral hygiene kits and branded personalized oral health information. GoodMouth also aims to improve America’s dental health through its Giving Goodness program. Organization Name: Gulf Coast African American Chamber of Commerce
Description: GCAACC was formed in 1999 by a group of business owners who desired to do business in the African American Community.
Full Description: The Gulf Coast African American Chamber of Commerce was formed in 1999 by a group of business owners who desired to do business in the African American Community, with a mission to provide the resources which will enable its members to prosper and be recognized as a community partner sharing in the wealth of The Gulf Coast (which includes Alabama, Mississippi, Florida and Louisiana). The Chamber is a member organization within the Gulf Coast business community and their members are united to create a unique central agency working to improve business and build a better community.  Their membership is composed of business, professional individuals and organization interested in prospering and creating a healthy environment in which to conduct business to ensure economic empowerment throughout the Greater Gulf Coast.  They are committed to developing, educating, and advocating for the growth of the economic status of their communities. The GCAACC is the only organization currently focused and positioned to meet the needs of the minority community relative to economic development.  Many of their major industries are downsizing or totally dissolving, which is causing more and more workers to choose to create their own businesses, therefore making GCAACC a vital part of their local economy. Through workshops, seminars, training, mentorship programs, consulting and technical assistance to their members, they will constantly strive to serve their members and fulfill their mission to promote and assist in community and economic development.  The focus of these events is to create civic, industrial, and commercial ventures that are diverse and reflect the views of the Gulf Coast community. Historically, chambers of commerce work with both public policymakers and the private sector to create livable, workable and equal communities.  History has not always proven people or events to be fair nor has it witnessed just and equitable policies, but moving forward they want to learn from history and THEY WILL NOT REPEAT those mistakes, both public and private.  They can’t afford the consequences for their future depends on it.

Full Description: We are a cloud-based service providing customers with personalized financial guidance that empowers customers to make more informed decisions about how to spend and invest their money. So if the user is relatively inexperienced, they will get the coaching they need.  If the user is an expert, they will be able to go quickly to the tools and features of interest to them.
